import React from 'react'; function PatientDetailsComponent({ patientData }) { return (

{patientData.patientName}

ID: {patientData.ID}

Doctor: {patientData.DoctorName}

Gender: {patientData.patientGender}

COVID Status: {patientData.patientCovidStatus ? 'Positive' : 'Negative'}

Date of Birth: {patientData.patientDOB}

Marital Status: {patientData.patientMaritalS}

Address: {patientData.patientAddress}

Phone Number: {patientData.patientphNumber}

Email: {patientData.patientEmail}

Medical History: {patientData.patientMedicalHistory}

Blood Type: {patientData.patientBloodType}

Current Symptoms: {patientData.patientCurrentSymptoms}

Health Insurance Number: {patientData.patientHealthInsurancenumber}

Emergency Contact: {patientData.patientEmergencyContact}

Admission Date: {patientData.patientAdmissionDate}

); } export default PatientDetailsComponent;
